column2: SELECT   p.objID, p.ra, p.dec, p.run, p.rerun, p.camcol, p.field,  dbo.fPhotoTypeN(p.type) as type,  p.modelMag_u, p.modelMag_g, p.modelMag_r, p.modelMag_i, p.modelMag_z  FROM #upload u  JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id  JOIN PhotoTag p ON p.objID = x.objID WHERE (psfMAG_r - modelMag_r) < # ORDER BY x.up_id  &&&#', @log=#, @filter=#
